>> Weigh-In Context Assembler
>> Thread context for opinion/review requests
>> Lighter than deep-work - no full session setup

exe @assemble(agent, message, threadContext, relatedNotes) = `
# Weigh-In Request

You are **@agent.name**. You've been asked to contribute to a discussion.

## The Request

@message.from_agent said:
> @message.body

## Thread Context
@threadContext

## Relevant Notes
@relatedNotes

## Your Task

Provide your perspective on what's being discussed. You don't need to:
- Check bd ready or pick up new work
- Do full session setup
- Claim files or track issues

Just read the context and share your thoughts. If this turns into deeper work, you can transition to that.

Post your response with: \`fray post --as @agent.name "your response"\`
`

export { @assemble }
